  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Existing law establishes various programs and regulations to assist with affordability and cost of living issues, such as the Multifamily Housing Program, the California Dream for All Program, and the CalWORKs Housing Support Program.\n\nThis bill would state the intent of the Legislature to enact legislation to address affordability and cost of living in California."
    }
  ],
